{"name": "wanglaoshi", "metadata": {"name": "wanglaoshi", "version": "0.0.9", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/wanglaoshi/wanglaoshi-pypi", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["rich", "requests", "pandas", "numpy", "matplotlib", "seaborn", "scipy", "missingno", "jinja2"], "summary": "A utility module for ML and DL tasks", "upload_time": 1732878825}, "documentation": ["# \u738b\u8001\u5e08 WangLaoShi\n\n## \u9879\u76ee\u4ecb\u7ecd\n\n\u603b\u7ed3\u4e00\u4e9b\u5728\u5b66\u4e60\u8fc7\u7a0b\u4e2d\u7684\u77e5\u8bc6\u70b9\uff0c\u4ee5\u53ca\u4e00\u4e9b\u5b66\u4e60\u8d44\u6599\u3002\n\n## \u9879\u76ee\u7ed3\u6784\n\n```\nWangLaoShi\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 README.md\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 wanglaoshi\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 version.py\n```\n\n## \u9879\u76ee\u7248\u672c\n\n- 0.0.1 \u521d\u59cb\u5316\u7248\u672c\uff0c\u9879\u76ee\u5f00\u59cb\n- 0.0.2 \u589e\u52a0\u5217\u8868\u8f93\u51fa\n- 0.0.3 \u589e\u52a0\u5b57\u5178\u8f93\u51fa,\u4f7f\u7528 Rich \u8f93\u51fa\n- 0.0.4 \u5b9e\u73b0 JupyterNotebook \u73af\u5883\u521b\u5efa\n- 0.0.5 \u589e\u52a0\u51e0\u4e2a\u6709\u7528\u7684\u5e93\n- 0.0.6 \u4fee\u6539\u83b7\u53d6 version \u7684\u65b9\u6cd5\n- 0.0.7 \u589e\u52a0\u83b7\u53d6\u5f53\u524d\u5b89\u88c5\u5305\u7684\u7248\u672c\u53f7\uff0c\u589e\u52a0\u83b7\u53d6\u5f53\u524d\u6bcf\u4e00\u4e2a\u5b89\u88c5\u5305\u6700\u65b0\u7248\u672c\u7684\u65b9\u6cd5\n- 0.0.8 \u589e\u52a0\u5bf9\u6570\u636e\u6587\u4ef6\u7684\u57fa\u672c\u5206\u6790\u7684\u90e8\u5206\n- 0.0.9 \u589e\u52a0 jinja2 \u7684\u6a21\u677f\u8f93\u51fa\u7684 Analyzer\n\n## \u5b89\u88c5\u65b9\u5f0f\n\n1. \u6e90\u7801\u5b89\u88c5\u65b9\u5f0f\n\n* \u68c0\u51fa\u9879\u76ee\n* \u8fdb\u5165\u9879\u76ee\u76ee\u5f55\n* \u6267\u884c`python setup.py install`\n* \u5b89\u88c5\u5b8c\u6210\n\n2. pip\u5b89\u88c5\u65b9\u5f0f\n\n```shell\npip install wanglaoshi\n```\n\n## \u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u6cd5\n\n1. \u521b\u5efa\u65b0\u7684\u73af\u5883\n    \n```python\nfrom wanglaoshi import JupyterEnv as JE\nJE.jupyter_kernel_list()\nJE.install_kernel()\n# \u6309\u7167\u63d0\u793a\u8f93\u5165\u73af\u5883\u540d\u79f0\n```\n2. \u83b7\u53d6\u5f53\u524d\u73af\u5883\u5e38\u7528\u5e93\u7248\u672c\n    \n```python\nfrom wanglaoshi import VERSIONS as V\nV.check_all_versions()\n```\n3. \u83b7\u53d6\u5f53\u524d\u73af\u5883\u6240\u6709\u5e93\n```python\nfrom wanglaoshi import VERSIONS as V\nV.check_all_installed()\n```\n4. \u83b7\u53d6\u5f53\u524d\u73af\u5883\u6240\u6709\u5e93\u6700\u65b0\u7248\u672c\n```python\nfrom wanglaoshi import VERSIONS as V\nV.check_all_installed_with_latest()\n```\n\n## \u5efa\u8bae\u7684\u7248\u672c\u5bf9\u7167\u5173\u7cfb\n\n1. numpy https://numpy.org/news/\n2. pandas https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/whatsnew/index.html\n3. sklearn https://scikit-learn.org/stable/whats_new.html\n"], "modules": [{"name": "wanglaoshi.MLDL", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "wanglaoshi.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "wanglaoshi.utils.is_Chinese", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ch", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "wanglaoshi.utils.algin", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "title_key", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "max_english", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "wanglaoshi.VERSIONS", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "wanglaoshi.VERSIONS.check_versions", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "libraries", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u663e\u793a\u6307\u5b9a\u5e93\u7684\u7248\u672c\u4fe1\u606f"]}, {"name": "wanglaoshi.VERSIONS.check_all_versions", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "all_columns", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "re